{"tid":1478960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等我幫你講一個唔去818集會嘅理由","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T12:01:28.000Z","uid":27780,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4085f5dbcdfe9a105432005552bf095dcbbb152","tid":1478960,"uid":27780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:07:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係你已經習慣及接受咗中國管治</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你接受咗上網講任何嘢都要自我審查<br />\n你接受咗喺街度唔敢表明自己立場<br />\n你懼怕著黑色衫出街<br />\n你懼怕帶上口罩<br />\n你習慣咗身邊發生嘅不公義嘅事<br />\n你習慣咗唔再相信身邊任何人<br />\n<br />\n你連去和平集會都怕被人清算<br />\n你自我選擇接受活喺白色恐怖之下<br />\n<br />\n恭喜您，你已經成為一個可以喺中共完全管治嘅地方生活。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">襯仲未為時已晚，睇一睇下面呢個post 再出發！<br />\n818見！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最期待的 反送中 懶人包出現了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478409\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478409</a>"},{"pid":"9bee9200ef2d468f82fbad205e9ef77222c8240d","tid":1478960,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"八一八 集會完後入機場！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e318078cf734dfeab80732386361f0891422278d","tid":1478960,"uid":27780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217a20895639e574d5aae5364883837e46164ef1","tid":1478960,"uid":27780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime